{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Well, they were old anyhow, so they said, in a-- philosophically, well, anyhow, we are old.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We-- we have to die anyhow, sooner or later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But at least the young ones will live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They-- they assumed that the young ones will be useful for Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because, I mean, many Germans were dead by then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they needed the workforce of the young people to-- to produce ammunition and spare parts for the German war effort.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So they were optimistic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The young ones will live, but we are finished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So that was the general idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Anyhow, one-- one morning I went over the next street to-- to find my girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the whole street was empty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that morning, at 5 o'clock, the SS-- the Gestapo-- came, and they drove them all to the trains.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it was the whole street, not one single-- the previous night, there were hundreds and thousands of people milling around.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was absolutely empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then, well, I never saw this girlfriend, of course, again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I was searching for her in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But probably she went straight to the gas chamber, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Anyhow, from then on, they picked up our brigade, 200 of us-- we were all strong young boys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And with the Hungarian Nazi-- you know, [NON-ENGLISH], which is the country police-- they're extremely cruel people, worse than the SS.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They was really sadistic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Anyhow, they ordered us to go from flat to flat, from house to house, and collect everything, what the departed people left behind.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So we went into these flats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And photo albums were lying all over the floor, and wedding photos, and all sorts of memories and items.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Of course, huge amounts of clothing-- well, everything that's in a normal flat.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
